sequenceDiagram
    %% View 01 — Terraform Execution
    %% Continues in: View 02 — OS-Level Configuration (provisioning-02-os.mmd)

    participant Dev as Developer
    participant TF as Terraform
    participant OCI as Oracle Cloud
    participant Net as OCI Network
    participant VMs as Compute Instances
    participant SSH as SSH Provisioner

    Note over Dev,TF: terraform apply

    TF->>OCI: Generate TLS RSA Key Pair
    
    Note over TF,Net: Provision Network Layer
    TF->>Net: Create VCN, Subnets, Gateway & Security
    TF->>Net: Configure VPN (IPSec & DRG)
    
    Note over TF,VMs: Provision Compute Nodes
    TF->>VMs: Create master.cdp (with cloud-init)
    TF->>VMs: Create node1-3.cdp (with cloud-init)
    OCI-->>VMs: Nodes provisioned & IPs assigned

    Note over TF,SSH: Upload Configuration Assets
    TF->>SSH: Connect via SSH to Master
    SSH->>VMs: Upload Blueprints, Playbooks & Scripts
    SSH->>VMs: Set execution permissions

    TF-->>Dev: Apply complete (Outputs: IP addresses)

    Note over TF,VMs: Cloud-Init execution begins asynchronously<br/>→ Continues in View 02
